Join Mussa in this endless run. Many obstacles will be at the way but our rapper has the help of special items and transports like the armored camel, a jet powered kibbe, a hoverboard inspired by Back To The Future, a fire spitting dragon, and many more.

The rapper’s saga goes beyond the village, crossing the scalding desert, facing the haters, overcoming the sandstorm, exploring a dark cave until arriving at the ruins of an ancient civilization where a gigantic Troll awaits to threaten who dares to show up.

To save Mussa’s fans you can equip the armored camel with many improvements achieved by earning experience and leveling up the camel. Armors, special powers and weapons are going to make your armored camel super powerful to let him support better your adventure.

Mussa’s visuals can be customized the way you want. There are thousands of combinations of accessories like goggles, masks, helmets, t-shirts and outfits you can choose from. Pick your visual and get ready to run with an amazing visual.

FEATURES
- Play with just a single touch on the screen
- 3D graphics
- Transports
- Character customization
- Leaderboards and achievements (Google Play Games)

Login with Google to unlock achievements and joining the leaderboards. What is the maximum distance you can reach? Are you able to score more than everybody else?

Join Mussa in this endless run. Many obstacles will be at the way but our rapper has the help of special items and transports like the armored camel, a jet powered kibbe, a hoverboard inspired by Back To The Future, a fire spitting dragon, and many more.

The rapper’s saga goes beyond the village, crossing the scalding desert, facing the haters, overcoming the sandstorm, exploring a dark cave until arriving at the ruins of an ancient civilization where a gigantic Troll awaits to threaten who dares to show up.

To save Mussa’s fans you can equip the armored camel with many improvements achieved by earning experience and leveling up the camel. Armors, special powers and weapons are going to make your armored camel super powerful to let him support better your adventure.

Mussa’s visuals can be customized the way you want. There are thousands of combinations of accessories like goggles, masks, helmets, t-shirts and outfits you can choose from. Pick your visual and get ready to run with an amazing visual.

FEATURES
- Play with just a single touch on the screen
- 3D graphics
- Transports
- Character customization
- Leaderboards and achievements (Google Play Games)

Login with Google to unlock achievements and joining the leaderboards. What is the maximum distance you can reach? Are you able to score more than everybody else?

Enjoy the adventure while Mussa sings some improvised rhymes. Start right now to save the fans with Mussa. He is counting on you!
